parts:
{
  "prompt": "A peaceful, intimate scene of two people sitting on brick platform near a small train station at sunset. One is a man in jeans and green sneakers, legs outstretched, and the other is a young woman with soft brown hair wearing a denim shirt, sitting close with her head resting gently on his shoulder. They are looking out at the tracks together, quietly waiting. The light is golden and warm. The setting is calm and deeply emotional. The station sign says 'Ashland, VA' in the background.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Clara sitting with Mark on the bricks at an outdoor train station during sunset, waiting for the train. Clara is drinking from a juice box and laughing so hard she can barely keep the juice in her mouth. They're relaxed, close together, with a soft golden sky and warm light. Mark is smiling, wearing jeans and green sneakers. Clara has shoulder-length hair, casual clothes, and loop-energy joy in her eyes.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "A peaceful, emotional scene on a train during golden hour. A man in a hoodie (Mark) sits by the window, calm and thoughtful. Next to him sits Clara, a soft-featured woman with a kind expression, resting her head gently on his shoulder while sipping from a juice box. Light filters through the window, bathing them both in warm sunset light. They are surrounded by quiet, with the outside world blurred in motion. Clara looks peaceful, Mark looks content. There is a sense of deep friendship and shared history between them.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Clara sitting by the window on a train looking at the sunset. She has soft features, a gentle expression, and shoulder-length hair. Mark is sitting next to her, wearing a hoodie, drinking from a juice box. The train interior is warm and softly lit, with golden sunset light streaming through the window. The mood is peaceful and intimate.",
  "size": "1024x1024"
}

{
  "prompt": "Clara sitting by the window on a train, watching the sunset. Mark is sitting next to her, drinking a juice box. The train is softly lit by golden light from the setting sun, and both of them are calm and content. Clara looks peaceful, Mark looks happy. The window reflects the orange-pink glow of the sky.",
  "size": "768x768"
}
